    "type": "monster",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Soldiers know memitims as the angels of death who protect fallen combatants and others who die as mass casualties from soul-hungry scavengers. While most memitims preside over massacres, their full wrath manifests against any who would cut numerous lives short in an unnatural pursuit of souls."
        }
    ],
